reck.annotation
Class MentionImpl

java.lang.Object
  reck.annotation.MentionImpl
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Cloneable, Mention
public class MentionImpl
extends java.lang.Object
implements Mention, java.lang.Cloneable, java.io.Serializable

A MentionImpl object acts as an Entity Mention that contains type/subtype/class, a set of entity mentions/ attributes corresponding to ACE 2004 definition.
